author: pdteam
info.description: An MX record was detected. MX records direct emails to a mail exchange server.

;; QUESTION SECTION:
;ants.gouv.fr.	IN	 MX
response:

;; OPT PSEUDOSECTION:

;; QUESTION SECTION:

ants.gouv.fr.	3600	IN	MX	5 mx1.ants.gouv.fr.
